\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531715\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531715\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104roz1665702891854.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/roz1665702891854.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/roz1665702891854.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"roz1665702891854\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Registering Type Libraries\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">For COM clients to locate and load an object, you need to register the object’s class in the Microsoft Windows Registry.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"roz1665702891854__context_w5766ab1b5b1_w5767ab1b5_w5768ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"roz1665702891854__topic_d35393e1_d35394e1_d35395e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"roz1665702891854__p_d35396e1_d35397e1_d35398e1\">The type information for the class is not copied to the Registry, but there are entries in the Registry that point to the type library file within the COM Interface DLL. These same entries indicate how to start the class’ server. When the COM Interface DLL is copied to a runtime workstation, you need to register the type library explicitly.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18137e1_d18138e1_d18139e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"roz1665702891854__p_d35399e1_d35400e1_d35401e1\">Use the standard Microsoft Windows\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">regsvr32.exe</span> program to register the required type library. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">regsvr32 servs.dll</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18140e1_d18141e1_d18142e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"roz1665702891854__p_d35402e1_d35403e1_d35404e1\">To unregister a type library, use the\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">/u</code> switch. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">regsvr32 /u servs.dll</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18143e1_d18144e1_d18145e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Create configuration definitions in the Registry using the Uniface COM Configuration utility.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18146e1_d18147e1_d18148e1\">To start the utility, choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uniface COM Configuration</span> from the Windows <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Start</span> menu, or run <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucomcfg.exe</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18149e1_d18150e1_d18151e1\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New</span> and provide a name for the definition.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18152e1_d18153e1_d18154e1\">Set the values for the configuration files and directories required by the application. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hig1665702753988.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hig1665702753988.html\" title=\"Specify the files and directories required by the Uniface application that COM connector needs to access.\">Settings for Selected Configuration Definition</a>.\n                          </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"roz1665702891854__li_d18155e1_d18156e1_d18157e1\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">OK</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Apply</span> to save the definition.\n </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"roz1665702891854__note_w5769ab1b5b3b5b3b3_w5770ab1b5b3b5b3_w5771ab1b5b3b5_w5772ab1b5b3_w5773ab1b5_w5774ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> For deployment within large organizations,<span class=\"ph filepath\">.reg</span>(registry) files can be used, or a third-party installation tool.</div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531715\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531715\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Registering Type Libraries Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Registering Type Libraries For COM clients to locate and load an object, you need to register the object’s class in the Microsoft Windows Registry. The type information for the class is not copied to the Registry, but there are entries in the Registry that point to the type library file within the COM Interface DLL. These same entries indicate how to start the class’ server. When the COM Interface DLL is copied to a runtime workstation, you need to register the type library explicitly. Use the standard Microsoft Windows regsvr32.exe program to register the required type library. For example: regsvr32 servs.dll Copy To unregister a type library, use the /u switch. For example: regsvr32 /u servs.dll Copy Create configuration definitions in the Registry using the Uniface COM Configuration utility. To start the utility, choose Uniface COM Configuration from the Windows Start menu, or run ucomcfg.exe . Click New and provide a name for the definition. Set the values for the configuration files and directories required by the application. For more information, see Settings for Selected Configuration Definition . Click OK or Apply to save the definition. Note: For deployment within large organizations, .reg (registry) files can be used, or a third-party installation tool. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}